#. Tag: title
#: details-currencies.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering transactions using different currencies"
msgstr "Introducir transacciones usando diferentes monedas"

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:174
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Whenever a transaction is entered that refers to more than one currency, "
#| "the exchange rate editor pops up and allows you to enter an exchange "
#| "rate. Initially, the current price available from the price database will "
#| "be used as exchange rate. See <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
#| "\">Entering exchange rates for currencies</link> for more information on "
#| "how to provide exchange rates manually and obtain online price "
#| "information."
msgid ""
"Whenever a transaction is entered that refers to more than one currency, the "
"exchange rate editor pops up and allows you to enter an exchange rate. "
"Initially, the most recent price available from the price database will be "
"used as the exchange rate. See <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
"\">Entering exchange rates for currencies</link> for more information on how "
"to provide exchange rates manually and obtain online price information."
msgstr ""
"Cada vez que se introduce un asiento que se refiere a más de una divisa, "
"aparece el editor de cotizaciones y le permite introducir esta. "
"Inicialmente, el precio actual disponible de la base de datos de precios "
"será utilizado como cotización. Vea <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
"\">Introducir cotizaciones para las divisas</link> para más información "
"sobre cómo proporcionar cotizaciones manualmente y obtener información sobre "
"precios en línea."

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally, the exchange rate is saved in the price database once entered by "
"the user."
msgstr ""
"Opcionalmente, la cotización se guarda en la base de datos de precios una "
"vez introducida por el usuario."

